title: With "Hotline Bling" Video, We've Reached Peak "Dominican Drake"
text:
Latinos on the Internet have long thought that Drake might secretly be Dominican. And it's not just some weird, half-baked theory. In fact, the team over at Remezcla is so convinced of "Dominican Drake" that they put together an entire history that charts the exact moment Drake started morphing into your Dominican uncle.
Now, with the release of Drake's video for "Hotline Bling," we've reached peak # DominicanDrake . Just take a look at the tweets and memes below, and tell me you're not convinced that Drake is really Latino, and Dominican, at heart. (He even got a shout-out from Romeo Santos, so you know he's legit.)
